==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Alphabetize
<hw>Al"pha*bet*ize</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>To arrange alphabetically; <as>as, to <ex>alphabetize</ex> a list
of words</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To furnish with an alphabet.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>alphanumerical</ent>⟦br⟧
